1
00:01:41,120 --> 00:01:41,880
He's here.

2
00:01:44,880 --> 00:01:45,520
Oh no.

3
00:01:46,280 --> 00:01:47,560
The Princess is trying to shake us off

4
00:01:47,560 --> 00:01:48,620
to go find someone.

5
00:01:54,880 --> 00:01:55,440
Aya?

6
00:01:56,920 --> 00:01:57,400
No.

7
00:01:57,759 --> 00:01:59,820
You're the Princess born from the AI.

8
00:02:01,120 --> 00:02:02,720
Aya didn't lie to me after all.

9
00:02:02,720 --> 00:02:04,520
A new personality has indeed been born.

10
00:02:04,520 --> 00:02:05,360
My Prince.

11
00:02:05,640 --> 00:02:06,370
Your destiny

12
00:02:06,760 --> 00:02:08,479
is bound to me forever.

13
00:02:11,280 --> 00:02:12,120
My dice.

14
00:02:14,040 --> 00:02:15,360
The memories of Buluotuo

15
00:02:15,360 --> 00:02:17,360
must be unlocked by the Prince and Princess together.

16
00:02:17,360 --> 00:02:18,000
I have been waiting for this day

17
00:02:18,000 --> 00:02:19,130
for a very long time.

18
00:02:19,160 --> 00:02:20,690
I won't let you leave again.

19
00:02:20,800 --> 00:02:21,600
I know.

20
00:02:21,920 --> 00:02:23,850
What you and I hate most is parting.

21
00:02:23,960 --> 00:02:25,800
That is why, a thousand years ago and a thousand years later,

22
00:02:25,800 --> 00:02:26,680
people have always sought

23
00:02:26,680 --> 00:02:27,920
the Tears of Buluotuo

24
00:02:28,079 --> 00:02:29,920
to stop the passing of life.

25
00:02:30,320 --> 00:02:31,120
Stay.

26
00:02:31,360 --> 00:02:32,240
Be with me.

27
00:02:32,520 --> 00:02:33,360
Stay here.

28
00:02:36,120 --> 00:02:37,640
Why don't you just lock me in a cage

29
00:02:37,640 --> 00:02:38,700
and keep me as a pet?

30
00:02:38,880 --> 00:02:39,880
Princess.

31
00:02:40,600 --> 00:02:42,560
How could you forget our promise?

32
00:02:43,120 --> 00:02:44,120
I have already found him.

33
00:02:44,120 --> 00:02:45,400
What use are you to me now?

34
00:02:45,400 --> 00:02:46,240
Luckily,

35
00:02:46,600 --> 00:02:47,720
I came prepared.

36
00:02:49,120 --> 00:02:50,450
Insignificant tricks.

37
00:02:53,920 --> 00:02:54,880
Having seen

38
00:02:55,160 --> 00:02:56,680
your skills before,

39
00:02:56,960 --> 00:02:58,720
how could I not take precautions?

40
00:02:58,720 --> 00:02:59,400
In a moment,

41
00:02:59,520 --> 00:03:01,180
once I have you under control,

42
00:03:01,480 --> 00:03:02,600
I can still obtain

43
00:03:02,840 --> 00:03:03,900
Buluotuo's Tears.

44
00:04:05,680 --> 00:04:06,810
Seize the Princess.

45
00:04:23,200 --> 00:04:24,400
Get out of here quickly.

46
00:04:24,400 --> 00:04:25,440
Otherwise, your consciousness

47
00:04:25,440 --> 00:04:26,560
will disappear with this collapsing

48
00:04:26,560 --> 00:04:27,760
virtual world.

49
00:04:51,120 --> 00:04:51,760
So,

50
00:04:52,760 --> 00:04:54,820
this is the final ending of the story.

51
00:04:56,080 --> 00:04:57,810
The prince saved the princess.

52
00:05:00,320 --> 00:05:00,960
I'm sorry.

53
00:05:02,160 --> 00:05:02,920
I lied to you.

54
00:05:04,440 --> 00:05:05,720
I am not a prince.

55
00:05:07,000 --> 00:05:08,860
Nor a reincarnation of ten lives.

56
00:05:09,680 --> 00:05:11,360
I'm just an ordinary person

57
00:05:12,200 --> 00:05:13,460
from the modern world.

58
00:05:15,040 --> 00:05:15,970
I got close to you

59
00:05:20,240 --> 00:05:21,920
just to find Buluotuo's Tear.

60
00:05:24,880 --> 00:05:26,720
But you still shielded me,

61
00:05:27,200 --> 00:05:28,560
just like a prince.

62
00:05:32,400 --> 00:05:33,040
Because

63
00:05:34,960 --> 00:05:36,560
in the real world,

64
00:05:37,200 --> 00:05:39,659
there's someone waiting for me to save them.

65
00:05:40,200 --> 00:05:42,000
Only by finding Buluotuo's Tear

66
00:05:43,760 --> 00:05:44,960
can I save her.

67
00:05:47,400 --> 00:05:48,320
So,

68
00:05:49,600 --> 00:05:51,260
you're sacrificing yourself

69
00:05:51,480 --> 00:05:52,560
for her?

70
00:06:04,920 --> 00:06:06,000
I understand.

71
00:06:08,120 --> 00:06:08,840
It turns out

72
00:06:10,240 --> 00:06:11,570
love isn't possession.

73
00:06:14,320 --> 00:06:15,200
It's sacrifice.
